283
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:09,240
I've realized that now...

284
00:11:11,080 --> 00:11:11,919
...you've really grown up.

285
00:11:15,120 --> 00:11:16,519
I... I'd rather hear that I've grown taller.

286
00:11:18,360 --> 00:11:19,000
Smells so good, so good.

287
00:11:19,000 --> 00:11:19,960
It really smells amazing.

288
00:11:19,960 --> 00:11:20,960
This slice of luncheon meat is mine. I'm starving.

289
00:11:20,960 --> 00:11:22,639
I reserved it. It has my name on it, nobody take it.

290
00:11:22,879 --> 00:11:23,440
I'm starving to death.

291
00:11:26,480 --> 00:11:27,919
It's not cooked yet. Wait for the pot to boil.

292
00:11:28,639 --> 00:11:29,120
Darn it, darn it.

293
00:11:30,200 --> 00:11:31,000
Take a sip, take a sip, take a sip.

294
00:11:31,279 --> 00:11:32,039
What do you want to eat?

295
00:11:32,519 --> 00:11:33,240
I want to eat tripe.

296
00:11:33,639 --> 00:11:34,200
If you ask me...

297
00:11:35,240 --> 00:11:36,240
...you guys are so efficient.

298
00:11:36,639 --> 00:11:37,360
Does that mean tomorrow...

299
00:11:37,360 --> 00:11:38,919
...we can hand the evidence over to the police?

300
00:11:39,440 --> 00:11:40,840
Not just the police side.

301
00:11:40,840 --> 00:11:41,759
We need to file a report.

302
00:11:42,240 --> 00:11:43,879
There are many other steps to take too.

303
00:11:44,080 --> 00:11:46,399
First, we go to the local notary office.

304
00:11:46,600 --> 00:11:48,320
To get all these posts notarized.

305
00:11:48,919 --> 00:11:50,159
You have to go there in person.

306
00:11:51,039 --> 00:11:52,759
Then go to the court to file a lawsuit.

307
00:11:52,919 --> 00:11:55,720
Requesting the real information of the infringer.

308
00:11:55,879 --> 00:11:56,919
If they provide it...

309
00:11:57,159 --> 00:11:58,200
...we'll settle before the trial.

310
00:11:58,440 --> 00:11:59,919
Then sue those who posted.

311
00:12:00,399 --> 00:12:02,720
These parts can be handled by a lawyer.

312
00:12:03,799 --> 00:12:04,200
So...

313
00:12:05,080 --> 00:12:06,879
Is the legal fee expensive?

314
00:12:07,320 --> 00:12:08,360
You don't need to worry about that.

315
00:12:08,559 --> 00:12:10,960
You can demand that those who hurt you...

316
00:12:10,960 --> 00:12:12,000
...cover your legal fees.

317
00:12:12,279 --> 00:12:13,960
It costs money to notarize the posts.

318
00:12:13,960 --> 00:12:14,840
You need to keep the invoices.

319
00:12:15,039 --> 00:12:17,639
And any costs incurred during the lawsuit...

320
00:12:17,639 --> 00:12:18,440
...keep the invoices for all of them.

321
00:12:18,759 --> 00:12:20,600
We'll make those bad guys reimburse you later.

322
00:12:21,320 --> 00:12:21,639
Okay.

323
00:12:22,559 --> 00:12:23,000
Sister Rui.

324
00:12:23,679 --> 00:12:24,360
You are so amazing.

325
00:12:24,879 --> 00:12:26,320
Did you secretly study law or something?

326
00:12:26,799 --> 00:12:27,200
Thank you for your hard work.

327
00:12:27,200 --> 00:12:27,799
Just eat.

328
00:12:27,960 --> 00:12:29,879
Here, Sister Rui, I'll eat more on your behalf.

329
00:12:30,440 --> 00:12:32,159
You need to keep a clear head at all times.

330
00:12:33,960 --> 00:12:35,200
I think I just scrolled past Wei Mingtian.

331
00:12:36,200 --> 00:12:37,879
It looks like he's clarifying things for Gui Fang.

332
00:12:43,120 --> 00:12:43,759
I just want to say...

333
00:12:43,919 --> 00:12:45,559
...what's being said online isn't true.

334
00:12:45,559 --> 00:12:47,120
Gui Fang is really a wonderful person.

335
00:12:47,240 --> 00:12:48,039
I was the one who dragged her into this.

336
00:12:48,159 --> 00:12:48,679
I hope you all...

337
00:12:48,679 --> 00:12:49,559
Stop pulling my hair.

338
00:12:51,519 --> 00:12:52,240
How many times have I told you?

339
00:12:52,600 --> 00:12:53,720
I told you not to get involved, not to get involved!

340
00:12:53,720 --> 00:12:55,159
You just had to stir up trouble for yourself, didn't you?

341
00:12:55,279 --> 00:12:56,840
Do you know what's most important right now?

342
00:12:56,919 --> 00:12:57,720
It's the truth.

343
00:12:58,919 --> 00:12:59,399
The truth?

344
00:12:59,519 --> 00:13:00,519
Does the truth pay your rent?

345
00:13:00,759 --> 00:13:01,960
Does the truth send you to college?

346
00:13:02,120 --> 00:13:03,120
Does the truth pay your tuition?

347
00:13:03,480 --> 00:13:04,360
Do you really think those people...

348
00:13:04,360 --> 00:13:05,480
...care what the truth is?

349
00:13:05,639 --> 00:13:06,279
Let me tell you.

350
00:13:06,399 --> 00:13:07,440
The truth right now is...

351
00:13:07,639 --> 00:13:09,120
...that you rely on the company for everything.

352
00:13:09,120 --> 00:13:09,919
You rely on me.

353
00:13:10,159 --> 00:13:10,840
I am the company.

354
00:13:10,919 --> 00:13:11,679
Then I quit.

355
00:13:12,039 --> 00:13:13,320
Anyway, I won't be an accomplice to this.

356
00:13:13,679 --> 00:13:14,200
I quit.

357
00:13:14,840 --> 00:13:15,360
Fine.

358
00:13:16,240 --> 00:13:17,000
You've seen the contract.

359
00:13:17,159 --> 00:13:18,279
You know how much the penalty is.

360
00:13:18,399 --> 00:13:19,200
You pay the compensation to them.

361
00:13:19,200 --> 00:13:19,960
I'm done earning this money.

362
00:13:20,360 --> 00:13:20,720
Get out.

363
00:13:22,720 --> 00:13:23,600
Look at you acting all tough.

364
00:13:24,320 --> 00:13:24,960
Starting a rebellion?

365
00:13:25,639 --> 00:13:26,559
I'm telling you, for the next two days...

366
00:13:27,399 --> 00:13:28,159
...don't go to school.

367
00:13:29,720 --> 00:13:30,399
As for work...

368
00:13:31,240 --> 00:13:32,200
...I'll pick you up and drop you off.

369
00:13:32,960 --> 00:13:33,639
You're not allowed to go anywhere.

370
00:13:34,200 --> 00:13:35,200
I'll ask for leave from the school.

371
00:13:41,399 --> 00:13:41,960
Ms. Kong,

372
00:13:42,080 --> 00:13:43,440
the platform has already provided us with

373
00:13:43,440 --> 00:13:44,960
the real information of the anonymous accounts.

374
00:13:45,080 --> 00:13:47,080
Based on the list we've compiled so far,

375
00:13:47,559 --> 00:13:48,480
the ones with the most serious impact

376
00:13:48,600 --> 00:13:50,039
are the operator of this account,

377
00:13:50,080 --> 00:13:50,960
named Zhao Chuyi,

378
00:13:51,159 --> 00:13:53,279
and the rumor mongers who posted the most initially,

379
00:13:53,679 --> 00:13:55,120
as well as a few leading accounts.

380
00:13:55,720 --> 00:13:57,799
Ms. Kong, let me confirm with you again.

381
00:13:58,120 --> 00:13:59,159
Regarding your request,

382
00:13:59,159 --> 00:14:00,840
do you wish to sue everyone?

383
00:14:00,840 --> 00:14:02,360
Or just sue these few?

384
00:14:04,480 --> 00:14:06,200
My child has already taken me to report it to the police.

385
00:14:06,480 --> 00:14:07,799
Can I still sue everyone?

386
00:14:12,320 --> 00:14:12,639
Hold on.

387
00:14:26,759 --> 00:14:27,240
It's like this.

388
00:14:33,679 --> 00:14:34,320
Of course you can.

389
00:14:34,440 --> 00:14:36,279
The police handle the public security punishment.

390
00:14:36,279 --> 00:14:36,559
Right.

391
00:14:36,559 --> 00:14:38,279
The court handles civil compensation.

392
00:14:38,279 --> 00:14:38,799
Yes.

393
00:14:38,799 --> 00:14:41,039
It's just that the waiting time might be longer.

394
00:14:41,200 --> 00:14:41,480
Right.

395
00:14:41,600 --> 00:14:42,120
So, do you...

396
00:14:42,360 --> 00:14:44,720
want everyone to bear your costs

397
00:14:44,720 --> 00:14:45,600
and demand compensation?

398
00:14:45,879 --> 00:14:47,840
Or mainly demand it from these few people?

399
00:14:49,240 --> 00:14:50,759
If you demand everyone to bear it,

400
00:14:50,759 --> 00:14:51,519
it's too scattered.

401
00:14:51,639 --> 00:14:52,440
And hard to enforce.

402
00:14:53,360 --> 00:14:54,360
Then let's just go with these few people.

403
00:14:54,639 --> 00:14:56,159
All costs will be borne by them.

404
00:14:56,320 --> 00:14:57,320
Is it okay if the others just apologize?

405
00:14:59,320 --> 00:14:59,799
Hold on.

406
00:15:04,840 --> 00:15:06,759
I'm not very close with her either.

407
00:15:11,279 --> 00:15:12,159
Let me summarize.

408
00:15:12,480 --> 00:15:13,360
All posters

409
00:15:13,519 --> 00:15:15,279
need to delete the defamatory posts

410
00:15:15,279 --> 00:15:16,919
and publicly apologize to Ms. Kong.

411
00:15:16,919 --> 00:15:17,240
Right.

412
00:15:17,759 --> 00:15:18,240
These few people

413
00:15:18,639 --> 00:15:21,200
need to bear your litigation fees, legal fees,

414
00:15:21,200 --> 00:15:22,919
notarization fees, and emotional distress damages.

415
00:15:22,919 --> 00:15:23,519
Yes. Is that okay?

416
00:15:23,799 --> 00:15:24,240
Is that okay?

417
00:15:29,240 --> 00:15:31,960
Will this punishment go into their permanent records?

418
00:15:34,080 --> 00:15:34,559
This...

419
00:15:34,799 --> 00:15:36,960
might depend on how the school handles it.

420
00:15:37,559 --> 00:15:38,000
Also,

421
00:15:38,279 --> 00:15:39,919
I still suggest you contact

422
00:15:39,919 --> 00:15:40,879
the other involved party,

423
00:15:40,879 --> 00:15:41,679
Mr. Wei Mingtian.

424
00:15:42,000 --> 00:15:43,679
If you can act as co-plaintiffs

425
00:15:43,679 --> 00:15:44,440
and sue together,

426
00:15:44,960 --> 00:15:46,759
it will definitely further expand the impact.

427
00:15:46,879 --> 00:15:47,200
Yes.

428
00:15:48,759 --> 00:15:49,679
Let's not do that.

429
00:15:50,080 --> 00:15:51,279
Don't drag him into this anymore.

430
00:15:51,440 --> 00:15:52,639
Otherwise, it'll just get more confusing.

431
00:15:53,120 --> 00:15:54,919
Actually, I tried contacting him.

432
00:15:55,240 --> 00:15:57,080
But his phone either goes unanswered

433
00:15:57,080 --> 00:15:58,120
or is just turned off.

434
00:15:58,679 --> 00:15:59,679
I don't know what's going on.

435
00:16:05,519 --> 00:16:06,279
Thank you, thank you.

436
00:16:06,399 --> 00:16:07,000
You're welcome.

437
00:16:07,279 --> 00:16:08,240
I didn't really help much.

438
00:16:08,360 --> 00:16:09,480
Just used a bit of data.

439
00:16:45,639 --> 00:16:46,120
Where are you going?

440
00:16:49,799 --> 00:16:50,480
Brother Maizi.

441
00:16:51,759 --> 00:16:53,840
I have a teacher who is very strict.

442
00:16:54,399 --> 00:16:56,360
Three leaves count as one absence.

443
00:16:56,679 --> 00:16:58,039
I really have to go to class today.

444
00:16:59,360 --> 00:17:01,080
Isn't this a special situation?

445
00:17:02,080 --> 00:17:03,799
The teacher will surely understand.

446
00:17:05,039 --> 00:17:05,480
For the next couple of days,

447
00:17:05,480 --> 00:17:06,680
stop thinking about classes.

448
00:17:07,279 --> 00:17:08,359
In about half an hour,

449
00:17:08,559 --> 00:17:09,759
go put on a face mask.

450
00:17:10,480 --> 00:17:11,480
Your skin isn't looking too good.

451
00:17:11,960 --> 00:17:13,799
Focus your mind on work, right?

452
00:17:14,480 --> 00:17:15,039
Yes.

453
00:17:17,119 --> 00:17:17,799
Brother Maizi.

454
00:17:19,599 --> 00:17:21,799
I think you're absolutely right.

455
00:17:22,599 --> 00:17:24,160
Lately, I...

456
00:17:24,160 --> 00:17:25,880
I'll just focus wholeheartedly on work.

457
00:17:26,240 --> 00:17:27,680
I won't go to school for now.

458
00:17:29,799 --> 00:17:30,440
Why are you pushing me?

459
00:17:30,440 --> 00:17:31,200
I want to sit right here.

460
00:17:31,839 --> 00:17:32,759
And why are you shouting?

461
00:17:32,960 --> 00:17:33,440
I...

462
00:17:35,319 --> 00:17:35,799
It's just...

463
00:17:36,200 --> 00:17:37,279
My dialogue teacher said...

464
00:17:37,720 --> 00:17:39,279
that even in daily life,

465
00:17:39,559 --> 00:17:41,319
we should keep practicing our lines.

466
00:17:41,720 --> 00:17:42,880
That way, when we get on stage,

467
00:17:42,880 --> 00:17:45,519
interacting with the partner will be more natural.

468
00:17:45,799 --> 00:17:46,519
You should have told me sooner.

469
00:17:46,519 --> 00:17:48,000
I could've just been your partner.

470
00:17:49,000 --> 00:17:50,839
Let's practice, let's practice, let's practice.

471
00:17:53,559 --> 00:17:56,039
It's good that you figured it out.

472
00:17:56,519 --> 00:17:57,079
Tell me,

473
00:17:57,319 --> 00:17:59,319
isn't going to school just for getting a good job?

474
00:17:59,599 --> 00:18:02,279
And now you already have a good job.

475
00:18:02,279 --> 00:18:04,079
So why bother going to school?

476
00:18:04,240 --> 00:18:04,640
Right?

477
00:18:04,640 --> 00:18:05,160
Yeah.

478
00:18:06,359 --> 00:18:09,440
Don't worry, I'll work hard.

479
00:18:09,880 --> 00:18:11,319
I'm not going anywhere.

480
00:18:12,039 --> 00:18:13,759
That's not necessary either.

481
00:18:14,279 --> 00:18:14,880
Recently,

482
00:18:15,319 --> 00:18:16,440
I was thinking about

483
00:18:16,640 --> 00:18:19,160
booking you for a couple of variety shows.

484
00:18:19,880 --> 00:18:21,279
Let's keep the hype up.

485
00:18:21,279 --> 00:18:21,880
No need.

486
00:18:22,559 --> 00:18:24,559
I appreciate your kindness.

487
00:18:24,839 --> 00:18:26,079
Appreciate what?

488
00:18:26,200 --> 00:18:27,519
This is your job.

489
00:18:27,839 --> 00:18:29,000
I just feel that...

490
00:18:29,279 --> 00:18:31,839
too much exposure recently isn't good.

491
00:18:32,200 --> 00:18:32,799
Makes sense.

492
00:18:33,079 --> 00:18:35,640
The internet hasn't been peaceful lately.

493
00:18:36,039 --> 00:18:37,240
So no variety shows.

494
00:18:37,640 --> 00:18:38,359
Forget it, forget it.

495
00:18:38,599 --> 00:18:39,759
Better to keep a low profile.

496
00:18:40,200 --> 00:18:40,799
Okay.

497
00:18:42,559 --> 00:18:44,839
If we get into a lawsuit...

498
00:18:44,839 --> 00:18:45,319
you know?

499
00:18:45,559 --> 00:18:46,279
Surely...

500
00:18:47,240 --> 00:18:48,640
we'll be on all kinds of trending topics.

501
00:18:48,640 --> 00:18:49,039
Exactly.

502
00:18:49,039 --> 00:18:50,599
It will definitely blow up.

503
00:18:51,039 --> 00:18:53,279
So, keeping a low profile is better.

504
00:18:53,759 --> 00:18:54,640
Good that you understand.

505
00:18:54,880 --> 00:18:56,200
It seems your dialogue skills

506
00:18:56,359 --> 00:18:58,240
have made significant progress.

507
00:18:58,440 --> 00:19:00,240
But you are still young.

508
00:19:00,359 --> 00:19:01,960
The road ahead is long and hard.

509
00:19:01,960 --> 00:19:02,519
Alright.

510
00:19:03,880 --> 00:19:06,599
Brother Maizi, I'll go put on a mask now.

511
00:19:07,079 --> 00:19:08,319
You sit here by yourself.

512
00:19:09,000 --> 00:19:09,359
Okay.

513
00:19:09,359 --> 00:19:09,960
I'm leaving now.

514
00:19:10,240 --> 00:19:10,640
Go ahead.

515
00:19:10,759 --> 00:19:11,400
Say no more.

516
00:19:11,519 --> 00:19:12,000
Go.

517
00:19:12,240 --> 00:19:13,400
Go, good boy.

518
00:19:18,359 --> 00:19:19,240
Pour me a glass of water.

519
00:19:19,400 --> 00:19:20,319
Pour one for yourself too.

520
00:19:27,359 --> 00:19:29,119
The kid wants to do stage plays recently.

521
00:19:30,839 --> 00:19:32,079
The stage builds character, but...

522
00:19:33,400 --> 00:19:34,680
the money comes too slow.

523
00:19:35,640 --> 00:19:37,279
This is too hard on the agent.

524
00:19:40,759 --> 00:19:41,400
Xiaotian.

525
00:19:43,240 --> 00:19:45,039
Pause your dialogue lessons for a couple of days.

526
00:19:45,799 --> 00:19:48,119
It's hard to get TV roles if your lines are too good.

527
00:19:52,440 --> 00:19:53,680
Excuse me, classmate, coming through.

528
00:20:03,039 --> 00:20:04,039
This is Donghu Police Station.

529
00:20:04,200 --> 00:20:05,720
Gui Fang has sued you. Come by when you have time.

530
00:20:07,599 --> 00:20:08,079
What's wrong?

531
00:20:08,279 --> 00:20:08,960
For real?

532
00:20:09,160 --> 00:20:10,440
Gui Fang actually sued me.

533
00:20:10,519 --> 00:20:11,160
What?

534
00:20:12,279 --> 00:20:13,799
They said I need to go over there too.

535
00:20:13,839 --> 00:20:15,759
But I just reposted it, that's all.

536
00:20:16,000 --> 00:20:17,400
How am I involved?

537
00:20:17,599 --> 00:20:18,920
I only reposted one thing.

538
00:20:19,680 --> 00:20:20,799
Yeah, they told me to go too.

539
00:20:21,400 --> 00:20:22,119
Hello?

540
00:20:24,400 --> 00:20:26,000
I just reposted it, that's all.

541
00:20:26,599 --> 00:20:27,599
I'll have a stain on my record.

542
00:20:27,680 --> 00:20:28,680
Then how will I find a job?

543
00:20:28,680 --> 00:20:29,519
Hurry up and check.

544
00:20:29,519 --> 00:20:30,519
Is it that serious?

545
00:20:31,200 --> 00:20:32,920
Is it really necessary just for saying a few words about her?

546
00:20:35,359 --> 00:20:37,240
It is. Of course it is.

547
00:20:37,799 --> 00:20:39,039
People live for their dignity.

548
00:20:39,279 --> 00:20:40,960
If you don't fight for your own dignity,

549
00:20:41,079 --> 00:20:41,960
who can you count on?

550
00:20:43,119 --> 00:20:43,480
Okay.

551
00:20:44,599 --> 00:20:45,440
I know about this now.

552
00:20:48,920 --> 00:20:50,359
The school takes this matter very seriously too.

553
00:20:53,079 --> 00:20:54,160
Gui Fang, all I can say is...

554
00:20:55,480 --> 00:20:56,240
the school's position...

555
00:20:56,920 --> 00:20:58,039
is definitely to protect the students.

556
00:21:02,519 --> 00:21:03,119
No, no, no.

557
00:21:03,559 --> 00:21:03,759
No.

558
00:21:04,279 --> 00:21:05,839
Why, why, why is she suing us?

559
00:21:06,200 --> 00:21:07,480
We're victims too!

560
00:21:08,559 --> 00:21:09,400
I don't know.

561
00:21:10,279 --> 00:21:12,160
Maybe she's mad at me.

562
00:21:12,240 --> 00:21:13,640
What kind of temper is that?

563
00:21:14,039 --> 00:21:15,400
Brother Maizi, you don't know her.

564
00:21:15,640 --> 00:21:17,039
Gui Fang is really resilient.

565
00:21:17,480 --> 00:21:18,599
She's someone who used just one year

566
00:21:18,599 --> 00:21:20,079
to raise her math score from the teens

567
00:21:20,079 --> 00:21:21,599
to over a hundred points.

568
00:21:22,240 --> 00:21:23,200
She's quite remarkable.

569
00:21:23,319 --> 00:21:25,160
And she won't give up easily.

570
00:21:25,160 --> 00:21:26,480
Unless she sees a result.

571
00:21:26,640 --> 00:21:28,599
You... you... you... you really are...

572
00:21:29,359 --> 00:21:30,640
Why did you provoke her?

573
00:21:31,640 --> 00:21:32,440
Look, look, look.

574
00:21:33,039 --> 00:21:33,880
It's number three on the trending list.

575
00:21:34,480 --> 00:21:36,440
Do you know what trending number three means?

576
00:21:38,359 --> 00:21:40,079
What does trending number three mean?

577
00:21:41,640 --> 00:21:42,880
This is a good thing!

578
00:21:44,079 --> 00:21:45,640
I can even raise your price.

579
00:21:46,839 --> 00:21:48,160
That's right, seriously.

580
00:21:49,440 --> 00:21:50,880
I got dragged in by your emotions.

581
00:21:52,720 --> 00:21:53,680
What a great opportunity.

582
00:21:54,000 --> 00:21:55,799
Come on, give me your classmate's number.

583
00:21:55,920 --> 00:21:56,640
What's her name again?

584
00:21:57,160 --> 00:21:57,960
Gui... Gui Fang.

585
00:21:57,960 --> 00:21:58,839
Give me the phone number.

586
00:21:59,039 --> 00:21:59,759
I'll contact her.

587
00:22:00,160 --> 00:22:01,119
Right now...

588
00:22:01,400 --> 00:22:02,319
this is the best...

589
00:22:03,039 --> 00:22:03,920
chance to operate.

590
00:22:04,720 --> 00:22:06,160
We'll go with her...

591
00:22:06,880 --> 00:22:07,799
to the court...

592
00:22:07,799 --> 00:22:09,559
and let the state uphold justice for us.

593
00:22:09,960 --> 00:22:11,480
We'll take the moral high ground

594
00:22:11,480 --> 00:22:12,279
and just stand there.

595
00:22:13,880 --> 00:22:16,319
Then your status will shoot right up.

596
00:22:16,720 --> 00:22:17,400
Yeah, yeah.

597
00:22:17,759 --> 00:22:18,920
Brother Maizi, you're so smart.

598
00:22:19,400 --> 00:22:20,279
You know, you...

599
00:22:20,400 --> 00:22:21,599
still have a lot to learn.

600
00:22:22,240 --> 00:22:23,480
In the entertainment industry...

601
00:22:23,480 --> 00:22:25,279
the art of turning danger into safety...

602
00:22:25,880 --> 00:22:26,880
bringing the dead back to... What are you doing?

603
00:22:28,000 --> 00:22:28,640
The phone number, right?

604
00:22:30,440 --> 00:22:31,839
Xiaoyin, I'm here, I'm here.

605
00:22:32,160 --> 00:22:33,039
I'm waiting for you right here.

606
00:22:40,559 --> 00:22:40,920
Hello.

607
00:22:41,640 --> 00:22:42,799
Can I have a word with you?

608
00:22:43,440 --> 00:22:44,160
You are?

609
00:22:44,640 --> 00:22:45,640
I'm Zhao Chuyi, a senior.

610
00:22:46,440 --> 00:22:48,319
I'll post a clarification and publicly apologize to you.

611
00:22:48,799 --> 00:22:49,480
Please drop the lawsuit.

612
00:22:49,839 --> 00:22:50,960
Can you please not make me go to the police station?

613
00:22:59,640 --> 00:23:01,519
You're the one behind the Duda Confessions account. You...

614
00:23:09,200 --> 00:23:10,240
What you're doing is wrong.

615
00:23:11,240 --> 00:23:12,680
Apologizing and deleting the post are mandatory.

616
00:23:13,079 --> 00:23:14,359
But you also have to take responsibility

617
00:23:14,359 --> 00:23:15,000
for what you've done.

618
00:23:15,279 --> 00:23:16,599
I will. I definitely will.

619
00:23:17,240 --> 00:23:18,480
This is the money from my part-time job this month.

620
00:23:18,759 --> 00:23:20,440
I'll give you my whole paycheck next month too.

621
00:23:21,079 --> 00:23:21,960
I run this account

622
00:23:21,960 --> 00:23:23,240
just to earn some tips.

623
00:23:23,720 --> 00:23:24,640
My mom is in poor health.

624
00:23:25,279 --> 00:23:27,000
Monthly medical bills have drained the family.

625
00:23:27,279 --> 00:23:28,039
I can't count on my dad.

626
00:23:29,160 --> 00:23:30,400
I know I was wrong this time.

627
00:23:31,039 --> 00:23:32,440
But I just don't want my mom to know.

628
00:23:35,920 --> 00:23:36,720
I'm afraid she'll be sad.

629
00:23:39,839 --> 00:23:41,119
It hasn't been easy for you, kid.

630
00:23:42,240 --> 00:23:43,079
You think you're the only one with a hard life?

631
00:23:46,279 --> 00:23:47,240
Life isn't easy for anyone.

632
00:23:47,519 --> 00:23:48,000
Just because you're struggling

633
00:23:48,000 --> 00:23:49,640
doesn't mean you can guilt-trip others here, right?

634
00:23:49,960 --> 00:23:50,920
Let me tell you something.

635
00:23:51,240 --> 00:23:52,240
Even for the sake of argument,

636
00:23:52,519 --> 00:23:53,839
even if your life is really that tragic,

637
00:23:54,079 --> 00:23:55,720
you can't make money by exploiting others.

638
00:23:55,960 --> 00:23:57,160
Is that how your mother raised you?

639
00:24:04,839 --> 00:24:05,440
I'm sorry.

640
00:24:16,559 --> 00:24:19,000
Gui Fang, I was simply amazing just now.

641
00:24:19,160 --> 00:24:20,240
That was simply the most...

642
00:24:20,240 --> 00:24:21,799
...successful argument of my life.

643
00:24:23,519 --> 00:24:24,759
Let's go, eat something good to celebrate.

644
00:24:25,240 --> 00:24:25,559
Let's go.

645
00:24:27,720 --> 00:24:29,160
That was so satisfying.

646
00:24:31,759 --> 00:24:33,480
Classmate, take a look at our Haidu Media.

647
00:24:34,559 --> 00:24:35,680
Classmate, check it out.

648
00:24:35,839 --> 00:24:36,240
Classmate.

649
00:24:36,759 --> 00:24:37,160
Classmate.

650
00:24:38,039 --> 00:24:39,680
It's okay, there's probably no one here.

651
00:24:39,680 --> 00:24:40,400
Why don't you rest for a while?

652
00:24:42,000 --> 00:24:42,400
Classmate.

653
00:24:42,559 --> 00:24:43,400
Please take a look.

654
00:24:43,920 --> 00:24:44,400
Classmate, Auntie.

655
00:24:45,079 --> 00:24:45,839
I am the one...

656
00:24:45,960 --> 00:24:47,799
...who reposted a post online.

657
00:24:48,240 --> 00:24:49,559
But I really had no bad intentions.

658
00:24:49,680 --> 00:24:50,920
I just used inappropriate words.

659
00:24:51,039 --> 00:24:51,680
Just following the trend.

660
00:24:51,799 --> 00:24:52,400
Please drop the lawsuit, Auntie.

661
00:24:52,400 --> 00:24:54,000
Auntie, I didn't mean to either.

662
00:24:54,039 --> 00:24:55,720
My parents sold everything to send me to college.

663
00:24:55,720 --> 00:24:57,279
My family is poor to begin with.

664
00:24:57,799 --> 00:24:58,279
Gui Fang.

665
00:24:58,599 --> 00:25:00,000
It's me, Senior Cao.

666
00:25:00,000 --> 00:25:01,079
I-I-I just reposted it.

667
00:25:01,079 --> 00:25:02,119
How can you be so heartless?

668
00:25:02,200 --> 00:25:03,680
My dad was just diagnosed with cancer last month.

669
00:25:03,720 --> 00:25:05,119
He's just hoping I graduate well and find a good job.

670
00:25:05,119 --> 00:25:06,200
How can I explain this to him?

671
00:25:06,200 --> 00:25:07,720
My mom passed away right after I got into Duda.

672
00:25:07,720 --> 00:25:09,559
In the hospital, she hoped I would graduate well.

673
00:25:09,559 --> 00:25:11,000
So what am I supposed to do now?

674
00:25:11,000 --> 00:25:12,319
You should have some basic logic when playing the victim.

675
00:25:12,799 --> 00:25:14,799
You said your dad runs every morning and is fit as a fiddle.

676
00:25:16,759 --> 00:25:19,839
Don't fight, don't fight, don't fight.

677
00:25:19,960 --> 00:25:22,680
Stop fighting, the Student Union will deduct credits.

678
00:25:28,960 --> 00:25:29,319
Mom.

679
00:25:30,160 --> 00:25:30,920
Mom, get up.

680
00:25:31,440 --> 00:25:32,000
What are you doing?

681
00:25:33,839 --> 00:25:34,319
Get up.

682
00:25:35,119 --> 00:25:35,960
Alright, stop fighting.

683
00:25:39,079 --> 00:25:40,160
Get up. Fighting...

684
00:25:40,839 --> 00:25:41,519
What are you doing?

685
00:25:47,200 --> 00:25:48,279
Writing so much here...

686
00:25:50,640 --> 00:25:54,920
People like this are just trying to grab attention.

687
00:25:55,400 --> 00:25:56,400
We probably don't need to...

688
00:26:01,599 --> 00:26:01,960
Mom.

689
00:26:03,440 --> 00:26:04,319
Look at the situation now.

690
00:26:04,759 --> 00:26:05,839
These young people...

691
00:26:06,319 --> 00:26:07,720
They're all like this, following the trend.

692
00:26:08,440 --> 00:26:09,759
I... I also follow trends when I'm bored.

693
00:26:09,920 --> 00:26:10,640
Exactly, exactly.

694
00:26:10,799 --> 00:26:11,799
Yes, it's not good either.

695
00:26:11,799 --> 00:26:12,599
But...

696
00:26:13,240 --> 00:26:14,359
It's not that serious, right?

697
00:26:14,720 --> 00:26:17,000
Let's just catch the first few people...

698
00:26:17,039 --> 00:26:18,079
The ones who started rumors and took photos.

699
00:26:18,079 --> 00:26:18,920
We just sue them.

700
00:26:19,200 --> 00:26:19,599
No.

701
00:26:21,079 --> 00:26:22,319
Following the trend makes them perpetrators too.

702
00:26:23,359 --> 00:26:24,000
Yes, but... but...

703
00:26:24,160 --> 00:26:25,759
We can't guarantee, right?

704
00:26:25,839 --> 00:26:28,319
Whether among these people there are some with bad intentions.

705
00:26:28,440 --> 00:26:29,680
People who hold a grudge.

706
00:26:29,960 --> 00:26:31,000
What if they pull some dirty tricks?

707
00:26:31,240 --> 00:26:32,160
Wouldn't we be at a disadvantage?

708
00:26:32,240 --> 00:26:33,359
There's no need, let's just avoid it.

709
00:26:33,519 --> 00:26:34,680
How can you say that?

710
00:26:35,000 --> 00:26:36,839
Good people get hurt and have to be careful everywhere?

711
00:26:37,160 --> 00:26:38,799
While bad people go unpunished and swagger around?

712
00:26:39,000 --> 00:26:40,039
You are aiding and abetting evil.

713
00:26:41,519 --> 00:26:43,119
You've heard of a thief stealing for a thousand days.

714
00:26:43,480 --> 00:26:44,680
Have you heard of guarding against a thief for a thousand days?

715
00:26:44,799 --> 00:26:45,519
Can we guard against them?

716
00:26:45,519 --> 00:26:46,160
Guard every day?

717
00:26:46,279 --> 00:26:47,680
That's why we must catch those thieves.

718
00:26:47,880 --> 00:26:48,799
Make them pay the price.

719
00:26:48,799 --> 00:26:49,480
So they dare not do it again.

720
00:26:49,720 --> 00:26:50,519
Fang, let's go.

721
00:26:53,759 --> 00:26:54,599
That's my mom.

722
00:26:56,359 --> 00:26:57,200
That's my mom.

723
00:26:57,839 --> 00:26:58,480
Would I really

724
00:27:00,200 --> 00:27:00,920
do anything to her?

725
00:27:14,599 --> 00:27:16,039
Don't be mad. Don't be mad.

726
00:27:16,559 --> 00:27:17,599
Don't lower yourself to his level.

727
00:27:17,599 --> 00:27:18,440
Don't hold it against him.

728
00:27:19,960 --> 00:27:20,960
Fang, let me show you something.

729
00:27:27,880 --> 00:27:29,079
Did you see what she's wearing today?

730
00:27:29,119 --> 00:27:30,480
Like an exploded shrimp cake.

731
00:27:31,599 --> 00:27:32,799
That jackfruit from Class 4.

732
00:27:32,799 --> 00:27:34,440
She seems to think she's so fashionable.

733
00:27:34,680 --> 00:27:35,799
Dressed so weirdly.

734
00:27:35,920 --> 00:27:36,960
It's really embarrassing.

735
00:27:37,400 --> 00:27:39,359
I started reading fashion magazines when I was little.

736
00:27:40,480 --> 00:27:41,200
When I was in middle school,

737
00:27:41,200 --> 00:27:43,079
I started trying to make my own clothes to wear.

738
00:27:43,880 --> 00:27:45,839
I made them and wore them myself; I didn't hurt anyone.

739
00:27:46,640 --> 00:27:47,640
But I don't know why,

740
00:27:48,559 --> 00:27:49,079
one day,

741
00:27:49,559 --> 00:27:51,079
suddenly someone on the school forum

742
00:27:51,079 --> 00:27:51,960
started a thread to mock me.

743
00:27:53,319 --> 00:27:54,359
I was too young back then.

744
00:27:54,640 --> 00:27:55,400
I didn't dare to fight back.

745
00:27:56,200 --> 00:27:57,079
Thinking about it now,

746
00:27:57,319 --> 00:27:58,599
I just feel very regretful.

747
00:27:59,119 --> 00:28:00,319
I should have grabbed them by the hair back then

748
00:28:00,319 --> 00:28:01,279
and fought them hard.

749
00:28:02,640 --> 00:28:03,039
Otherwise,

750
00:28:03,599 --> 00:28:04,839
this incident would just become a

751
00:28:04,839 --> 00:28:06,160
wound that will never heal for me.

752
00:28:07,160 --> 00:28:08,599
What they said was too much.

753
00:28:09,039 --> 00:28:10,599
Did your parents not handle this back then?

754
00:28:13,279 --> 00:28:15,160
My mom thought I was in the wrong first.

755
00:28:15,759 --> 00:28:17,559
Instead, she wouldn't let me touch the sewing machine anymore.

756
00:28:19,039 --> 00:28:20,960
My dad actually went to school to find the teacher.

757
00:28:21,880 --> 00:28:23,839
He also got a few boys to come out and apologize to me.

758
00:28:24,279 --> 00:28:25,720
But I knew they weren't sincere.

759
00:28:26,319 --> 00:28:27,519
Later, when they saw me at school,

760
00:28:27,519 --> 00:28:28,680
they would still make faces at me.

761
00:28:31,160 --> 00:28:31,480
Fang,

762
00:28:32,759 --> 00:28:34,519
just like among those people coming to apologize to you,

763
00:28:35,039 --> 00:28:36,559
some are seniors looking for jobs

764
00:28:36,559 --> 00:28:37,440
and don't want to get disciplined.

765
00:28:37,720 --> 00:28:39,200
They aren't truly repenting.

766
00:28:40,039 --> 00:28:40,519
Gui Fang,

767
00:28:42,039 --> 00:28:43,359
I don't want you to be like me

768
00:28:44,079 --> 00:28:45,279
and be left with a wound like this.

769
00:28:50,279 --> 00:28:51,720
Don't feel aggrieved. Don't feel aggrieved.

770
00:28:54,559 --> 00:28:55,279
No more feeling aggrieved.

771
00:29:33,240 --> 00:29:34,480
Hello, Auntie.

772
00:29:35,200 --> 00:29:36,519
We are here to apologize.

773
00:29:36,680 --> 00:29:36,960
Yes.

774
00:29:37,039 --> 00:29:39,400
We thought Xiaotian... that student...

775
00:29:39,640 --> 00:29:41,200
was being bullied.

776
00:29:41,200 --> 00:29:42,559
We were upholding justice.

777
00:29:42,759 --> 00:29:43,519
We were one-sided.

778
00:29:43,759 --> 00:29:45,319
We hope you can forgive us.

779
00:29:45,440 --> 00:29:45,799
Yes.

780
00:29:47,240 --> 00:29:48,240
You thought

781
00:29:49,039 --> 00:29:50,079
Wei Mingtian was being bullied?

782
00:29:50,680 --> 00:29:51,720
No, no, no.

783
00:29:51,720 --> 00:29:52,160
No, no.

784
00:29:52,160 --> 00:29:53,400
Where did you get that idea from?

785
00:29:55,200 --> 00:29:55,799
Besides,

786
00:29:56,079 --> 00:29:57,319
spreading rumors about me and helping him,

787
00:29:57,759 --> 00:29:58,960
is there any connection between the two?

788
00:30:00,559 --> 00:30:01,319
Look, Auntie,

789
00:30:01,319 --> 00:30:03,160
you can't be so unforgiving.

790
00:30:03,599 --> 00:30:05,079
Don't you just want us to apologize

791
00:30:05,319 --> 00:30:06,160
and pay you money?

792
00:30:06,160 --> 00:30:07,039
Stop talking.

793
00:30:07,200 --> 00:30:07,880
How much money do you want?

794
00:30:08,079 --> 00:30:09,200
We'll just pay you.

795
00:30:09,599 --> 00:30:10,240
We'll give it all to you.

796
00:30:10,640 --> 00:30:12,279
You... you can't be so ruthless.

797
00:30:12,400 --> 00:30:13,839
You can't let us actually get disciplined

798
00:30:13,839 --> 00:30:14,720
just so you'll be happy.

799
00:30:14,880 --> 00:30:15,880
Alright, stop talking.

800
00:30:16,559 --> 00:30:17,519
Um, Auntie,

801
00:30:17,720 --> 00:30:18,680
we didn't mean that.

802
00:30:18,880 --> 00:30:20,440
We are sincerely apologizing to you.

803
00:30:20,960 --> 00:30:22,319
Then we won't disturb you anymore.

804
00:30:22,920 --> 00:30:23,440
Get back to your studies.

805
00:30:23,920 --> 00:30:24,559
We're leaving now.

806
00:30:24,759 --> 00:30:25,079
Bye-bye.

807
00:30:25,680 --> 00:30:26,000
Bye-bye.

808
00:30:28,359 --> 00:30:29,240
Come here, come here.

809
00:30:29,839 --> 00:30:31,240
What are you two doing?

810
00:30:31,319 --> 00:30:32,240
Arguing with her like that.

811
00:30:33,119 --> 00:30:34,240
You, why were you so aggressive with her?

812
00:30:34,240 --> 00:30:35,079
No, she just... she...

813
00:30:37,160 --> 00:30:38,640
We can't suffer this loss for nothing.

814
00:30:39,240 --> 00:30:40,200
And besides, in the school,

815
00:30:40,279 --> 00:30:41,440
surely it's not just the three of us who hate her.

816
00:30:41,880 --> 00:30:43,559
We have to be steady, you know?

817
00:30:43,799 --> 00:30:44,599
Wait for this to blow over.

818
00:30:45,880 --> 00:30:47,079
We even bought a fruit basket.

819
00:30:48,240 --> 00:30:49,000
What a waste.

820
00:31:00,119 --> 00:31:00,720
Watch out.

821
00:31:15,880 --> 00:31:16,720
Student, are you okay?

822
00:31:18,200 --> 00:31:19,079
Careful, she might fake an injury.

823
00:31:19,079 --> 00:31:19,920
Watch out, she might sue you.

824
00:31:51,599 --> 00:31:51,880
No,

825
00:31:53,880 --> 00:31:56,559
yes, they were jumping on the bandwagon with their mockery.

826
00:31:56,880 --> 00:31:58,880
But don't stoop to their level.

827
00:31:59,039 --> 00:32:00,279
What if they didn't mean any harm?

828
00:32:00,599 --> 00:32:02,319
Who hasn't made a mistake before?

829
00:32:02,319 --> 00:32:03,559
Have you never badmouthed anyone?

830
00:32:06,160 --> 00:32:08,000
I... that's not what I meant.

831
00:32:11,799 --> 00:32:12,960
I just went through your Weibo.

832
00:32:14,640 --> 00:32:15,119
This post.

833
00:32:16,079 --> 00:32:16,680
And this one.

834
00:32:17,880 --> 00:32:18,960
Are these things you said?

835
00:32:20,519 --> 00:32:21,480
That was back when

836
00:32:21,640 --> 00:32:23,000
that happened, and I stepped in to help.

837
00:32:23,839 --> 00:32:24,960
Why... why are you digging up my past?

838
00:32:25,720 --> 00:32:28,200
Because I wanted to know if you jumped on the bandwagon too.

839
00:32:28,200 --> 00:32:30,359
If you also hurt others without realizing it.

840
00:32:30,799 --> 00:32:31,799
That's why you think

841
00:32:32,039 --> 00:32:33,880
those minor hurts don't matter.

842
00:32:34,960 --> 00:32:36,319
Anyway, I've never talked about others.

843
00:32:36,559 --> 00:32:37,400
Never been mean-spirited.

844
00:32:37,559 --> 00:32:38,839
And never judged anyone.

845
00:32:39,480 --> 00:32:40,440
From my perspective,

846
00:32:40,640 --> 00:32:41,400
people like me

847
00:32:41,400 --> 00:32:43,279
are the majority, the normal ones.

848
00:32:44,400 --> 00:32:46,160
If the remaining minority

849
00:32:46,160 --> 00:32:47,640
cannot restrain their words and actions,

850
00:32:48,640 --> 00:32:49,920
then let the law restrain them.

851
00:33:17,519 --> 00:33:18,000
What's wrong?

852
00:33:18,359 --> 00:33:18,640
Coach.

853
00:33:18,640 --> 00:33:19,119
What happened?

854
00:33:19,200 --> 00:33:19,960
You're finally here.

855
00:33:20,440 --> 00:33:21,839
Xu Rui has been running like this all night.

856
00:33:21,839 --> 00:33:23,200
I can't even stop her.

857
00:33:25,839 --> 00:33:26,200
Good.

858
00:33:27,480 --> 00:33:29,920
What a fighting spirit this is!

859
00:33:30,279 --> 00:33:31,160
Truly moving.

860
00:33:32,039 --> 00:33:32,480
Let me tell you,

861
00:33:32,599 --> 00:33:33,279
in her,

862
00:33:33,279 --> 00:33:34,880
I see a shadow of my younger self.

863
00:33:35,680 --> 00:33:36,559
No, Coach.

864
00:33:36,920 --> 00:33:38,640
She can't keep running like this.

865
00:33:38,640 --> 00:33:39,559
Shouldn't we

866
00:33:39,640 --> 00:33:41,240
increase the training intensity a bit?

867
00:33:42,200 --> 00:33:42,640
Makes sense.

868
00:33:43,240 --> 00:33:44,119
Very promising.

869
00:33:44,960 --> 00:33:45,440
But

870
00:33:45,519 --> 00:33:47,519
a person's stamina has a limit.

871
00:33:47,559 --> 00:33:49,559
You can't keep the training string too tight.

872
00:33:49,759 --> 00:33:52,160
If it's too tight, isn't she likely

873
00:33:53,839 --> 00:33:54,559
to get injured?

874
00:34:06,519 --> 00:34:07,559
Is your foot okay?

875
00:34:08,360 --> 00:34:09,440
It's just a scratch. I'm fine.

876
00:34:13,519 --> 00:34:15,199
Auntie, don't be sad.

877
00:34:15,960 --> 00:34:17,960
You were protecting your legitimate rights.

878
00:34:18,079 --> 00:34:19,199
It wasn't malicious revenge.

879
00:34:19,639 --> 00:34:21,239
Don't take their words to heart.

880
00:34:23,800 --> 00:34:24,599
I just feel that...

881
00:34:25,639 --> 00:34:26,840
because of this mess,

882
00:34:27,039 --> 00:34:28,400
caused you and Xiaocan to fight,

883
00:34:29,079 --> 00:34:30,920
and brought up bad memories for Xiaoyin.

884
00:34:32,039 --> 00:34:34,480
Is it worth turning a good life into a mess?

885
00:34:37,559 --> 00:34:38,400
I'm really tired.

886
00:34:39,400 --> 00:34:40,920
I just hope this blows over soon.

887
00:34:40,920 --> 00:34:41,719
Let's not make it any bigger.

888
00:34:42,320 --> 00:34:44,199
So everyone can live happily like before.

889
00:34:44,440 --> 00:34:45,000
Wouldn't that be nice?

890
00:34:50,079 --> 00:34:50,440
Gui Fang.

891
00:34:51,039 --> 00:34:51,599
Gui Fang! Gui Fang!

892
00:34:52,039 --> 00:34:52,559
Wait a second, Gui Fang.

893
00:34:53,480 --> 00:34:54,400
I really did it this time.

894
00:34:55,280 --> 00:34:56,320
I can finally help you too.

895
00:34:57,840 --> 00:34:58,960
You... what did you do?

896
00:35:00,400 --> 00:35:01,559
You're totally famous now.

897
00:35:03,599 --> 00:35:05,119
On the path of fighting cyberbullying,

898
00:35:05,159 --> 00:35:06,559
Ms. Kong has shown us

899
00:35:06,559 --> 00:35:08,199
unparalleled resilient spirit,

900
00:35:08,360 --> 00:35:10,079
becoming a role model for countless people.

901
00:35:10,679 --> 00:35:11,599
Let's also hear

902
00:35:11,599 --> 00:35:13,440
the public's opinion on this matter.

903
00:35:14,679 --> 00:35:15,320
Excuse me, student.

904
00:35:15,400 --> 00:35:16,800
What do you think about the recent events

905
00:35:16,800 --> 00:35:18,400
regarding Ms. Kong Gui Fang?

906
00:35:18,800 --> 00:35:19,760
You mean about Auntie Kong Gui Fang?

907
00:35:19,760 --> 00:35:20,360
Yes, yes.

908
00:35:20,360 --> 00:35:21,559
This matter has caused a sensation in society.

909
00:35:21,920 --> 00:35:22,360
I think

910
00:35:22,519 --> 00:35:23,639
this auntie did a great job.

911
00:35:23,880 --> 00:35:25,320
She taught me how to handle such things.

912
00:35:26,039 --> 00:35:26,960
First, collect evidence.

913
00:35:27,159 --> 00:35:28,039
Public prosecution, suing.

914
00:35:28,239 --> 00:35:29,920
Learn to use the weapon of law to protect oneself.

915
00:35:30,039 --> 00:35:31,559
This is what I learned from this matter.

916
00:35:32,000 --> 00:35:33,360
Finally, I want to say to the auntie:

917
00:35:33,760 --> 00:35:34,079
Auntie,

918
00:35:34,280 --> 00:35:35,400
you have elevated my understanding

919
00:35:35,559 --> 00:35:36,239
of the law.

920
00:35:36,679 --> 00:35:37,159
Go Auntie!

921
00:35:37,519 --> 00:35:38,800
Keep it up! I support you!

922
00:35:39,480 --> 00:35:39,840
Okay.

923
00:35:39,840 --> 00:35:41,920
Many thanks to our "Student Elevation."

924
00:35:42,159 --> 00:35:44,039
We strongly agree with his remarks.

925
00:35:44,239 --> 00:35:46,400
But his behavior on the escalator...

926
00:35:46,400 --> 00:35:48,360
we strongly advise against imitating.

927
00:35:48,599 --> 00:35:49,360
You're talking about Kong Gui Fang?

928
00:35:49,599 --> 00:35:50,159
Yes, yes.

929
00:35:50,320 --> 00:35:51,000
I was just watching it.

930
00:35:52,280 --> 00:35:53,119
Young people these days...

931
00:35:53,119 --> 00:35:54,199
they have no idea of the immensity of heaven and earth.

932
00:35:54,320 --> 00:35:55,119
Sir, don't get excited.

933
00:35:55,280 --> 00:35:56,760
If you ask me, they just... just... just...

934
00:35:56,880 --> 00:35:58,679
just have it too easy.

935
00:35:58,840 --> 00:35:59,719
Don't get excited, sir.

936
00:35:59,719 --> 00:36:00,480
They have nothing to do,

937
00:36:00,480 --> 00:36:01,760
so they think about bullying others.

938
00:36:02,280 --> 00:36:03,800
They should be punished by the law.

939
00:36:04,039 --> 00:36:04,840
Make them fear!

940
00:36:04,920 --> 00:36:05,639
Be afraid!

941
00:36:05,760 --> 00:36:06,840
Okay sir, please don't get excited.

942
00:36:07,039 --> 00:36:08,360
Thank you very much for supporting

943
00:36:08,360 --> 00:36:09,159
our interview.

944
00:36:11,559 --> 00:36:13,440
Okay, many thanks to "Mr. Excited"

945
00:36:13,440 --> 00:36:14,480
for his excited remarks.

946
00:36:14,679 --> 00:36:15,719
But his excited remarks

947
00:36:15,719 --> 00:36:17,400
have also brought Ms. Kong Gui Fang

948
00:36:17,400 --> 00:36:19,559
very strong support.

949
00:36:20,280 --> 00:36:20,639
Okay.

950
00:36:20,639 --> 00:36:22,960
Hope everyone follows and likes.

951
00:36:23,119 --> 00:36:23,719
Thank you, everyone.

952
00:36:24,519 --> 00:36:26,199
Did you hire a team to do this?

953
00:36:26,840 --> 00:36:27,760
You're so generous.

954
00:36:28,519 --> 00:36:29,000
It wasn't me.

955
00:36:29,400 --> 00:36:30,440
Brother Maizi contacted them.

956
00:36:31,440 --> 00:36:33,239
But he didn't let me film.

957
00:36:33,800 --> 00:36:34,639
It's a bit of a pity.

958
00:36:37,320 --> 00:36:38,800
They even did street interviews.

959
00:36:38,880 --> 00:36:40,119
That's so thoughtful.

960
00:36:40,719 --> 00:36:41,679
Brother Li Wai spoke well, right?

961
00:36:43,159 --> 00:36:43,679
And him too.

962
00:36:43,960 --> 00:36:44,480
Li Wai?

963
00:36:44,719 --> 00:36:45,400
Which one is him?

964
00:36:46,360 --> 00:36:47,119
They are all him.

965
00:36:54,360 --> 00:36:55,519
Hello, Professor Wang.

966
00:37:02,159 --> 00:37:02,639
Gui Fang.

967
00:37:03,920 --> 00:37:05,920
The TV station's program team came to the school.

968
00:37:07,159 --> 00:37:09,480
They proposed filming a special episode.

969
00:37:11,320 --> 00:37:12,400
So tomorrow,

970
00:37:13,119 --> 00:37:15,960
all students involved in this matter

971
00:37:16,280 --> 00:37:18,239
will be gathered in the lecture hall.

972
00:37:19,360 --> 00:37:22,039
The school hopes you can cooperate with the TV interview.

973
00:37:28,480 --> 00:37:29,480
I said before,

974
00:37:30,760 --> 00:37:33,079
the school's stance is always to protect the students.

975
00:37:35,000 --> 00:37:36,719
They are also students of the school.

976
00:37:45,079 --> 00:37:46,000
These are the Weibo posts they wrote.

977
00:37:46,360 --> 00:37:47,400
I plan to clap back at every single one.

978
00:37:47,559 --> 00:37:48,000
Take a look.

979
00:37:48,719 --> 00:37:49,440
Is my comeback good?

980
00:37:50,199 --> 00:37:51,239
Who's clinging to whom between us?

981
00:37:51,440 --> 00:37:52,320
I'm clinging to you, right?

982
00:37:53,239 --> 00:37:54,440
Do you think I'm too clingy?

983
00:37:54,440 --> 00:37:55,159
Are you calling me out?

984
00:37:55,599 --> 00:37:58,400
Why do you guys look even angrier than me?

985
00:37:58,760 --> 00:38:00,960
Gui Fang, I don't want you to end up like me,

986
00:38:01,679 --> 00:38:02,920
left with a wound like this.

987
00:38:10,760 --> 00:38:11,679
But Gui Fang,

988
00:38:13,039 --> 00:38:15,320
you don't have to do what anyone expects.

989
00:38:16,960 --> 00:38:18,119
I know that in your heart,

990
00:38:19,079 --> 00:38:20,360
you have your own sense of justice.

991
00:38:28,719 --> 00:38:29,719
Regarding this footage,

992
00:38:29,719 --> 00:38:30,880
we'll shoot the exterior again later...

993
00:38:30,880 --> 00:38:33,199
I told you the school would step in.

994
00:38:33,920 --> 00:38:35,519
After all, they are the school's students.

995
00:38:36,880 --> 00:38:37,639
The law can't punish the masses.

996
00:38:38,480 --> 00:38:39,519
We have to stick together.

997
00:38:40,440 --> 00:38:41,159
I know how this works.

998
00:39:15,280 --> 00:39:15,639
Okay.

999
00:39:16,039 --> 00:39:16,639
Student Kong,

1000
00:39:16,760 --> 00:39:19,039
how are you feeling right now?

1001
00:39:19,320 --> 00:39:21,039
Will you accept a settlement with your classmates?

1002
00:39:24,639 --> 00:39:25,960
If there are classmates today

1003
00:39:27,079 --> 00:39:28,199
who sincerely apologize to me,

1004
00:39:31,440 --> 00:39:31,960
I accept.

1005
00:39:33,360 --> 00:39:34,599
Yes, our Student Kong

1006
00:39:34,599 --> 00:39:36,320
is still very friendly.

1007
00:39:36,440 --> 00:39:36,960
And she also...

1008
00:39:37,079 --> 00:39:38,400
But regardless of whether they apologize,

1009
00:39:38,800 --> 00:39:40,199
I will not accept a settlement.

1010
00:39:42,599 --> 00:39:44,559
I believe the law and school regulations

1011
00:39:44,760 --> 00:39:46,360
will give me the fairest result.

1012
00:40:11,280 --> 00:40:12,960
I think this auntie did a great job.

1013
00:40:13,119 --> 00:40:14,960
Some people just have it too easy.

1014
00:40:14,960 --> 00:40:16,320
Go for it! I support you!

1015
00:40:19,559 --> 00:40:20,400
Is my hair okay?

1016
00:40:21,440 --> 00:40:22,039
It's fine.

1017
00:40:22,360 --> 00:40:23,119
I have experience with this.

1018
00:40:23,199 --> 00:40:24,000
I previously filmed

1019
00:40:24,679 --> 00:40:26,119
a promotional video for the Public Security Bureau.

1020
00:40:26,480 --> 00:40:26,920
I've got experience.

1021
00:40:26,920 --> 00:40:27,480
I'm a veteran actor.

1022
00:40:28,199 --> 00:40:29,760
They should be punished by the law!

1023
00:40:29,760 --> 00:40:30,559
Make them fear!

1024
00:40:30,679 --> 00:40:31,679
Fe- fear!

1025
00:40:31,679 --> 00:40:32,599
His passionate remarks

1026
00:40:32,599 --> 00:40:34,159
have also given Ms. Kong Gui Fang

1027
00:40:34,159 --> 00:40:35,360
strong support.

1028
00:40:35,840 --> 00:40:37,039
Let's interview

1029
00:40:37,079 --> 00:40:38,320
the next enthusiastic viewer.

1030
00:40:40,199 --> 00:40:41,239
Is there something wrong with you?

1031
00:40:41,440 --> 00:40:41,880
Let me see.

1032
00:40:43,519 --> 00:40:44,800
Look at the people you found.

1033
00:40:44,800 --> 00:40:45,199
No, no.

1034
00:40:45,199 --> 00:40:46,039
You smashed my phone like this.

1035
00:40:46,039 --> 00:40:46,440
Sister, I'm sorry.

1036
00:40:46,440 --> 00:40:48,079
Why did you get so excited?

1037
00:40:48,079 --> 00:40:49,239
I just got caught up in the emotion.

1038
00:40:49,239 --> 00:40:50,320
I... I didn't mean to.

1039
00:40:50,639 --> 00:40:51,559
I can't believe this.

1040
00:40:54,480 --> 00:40:55,599
Let Xiaotian buy you a new one.

1041
00:40:56,480 --> 00:40:57,400
You dropped it, you pay.
